  "description": "Brinjal Chutney or Kathirikai Chutney is a creamy and flavourful South Indian side dish made with roasted or sautéed brinjal, coconut, mustard, red chillies and tamarind. The smoky flavour from roasting the brinjal directly over flame gives this chutney a unique depth. It is a treat for brinjal lovers and pairs beautifully with idli and dosa.",
